data.description: Welcome to your eco-friendly Smart Home! This "almost new" home was built in 2020 and is situated on a desirable corner lot.  Smart Home features include Google Nest thermostats, Wi-fi enabled garage door openers, and smart lights. New carpet and paint throughout, and "almost new" washer and dryer conveys with home as well.  The spacious layout boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths with ample space for every member of the family.  The open floorplan seamlessly connects the kitchen and family room which can make for great entertaining.  The expansive corner lot can be used for a play area for the kids, a lush garden and for family cookouts.  Conveniently located to schools, parks, shopping, and amenities.  NO DOWN PAYMENT financing available for qualified buyers!
